{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png"}],"title":"Getting Started with Sloths","roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"title":"Essentials","anchor":"Essentials","generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name","isActive":true},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". You can optionally provide a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property"},{"text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth","text":"Create a Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"},{"text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of "},{"code":"ice","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"wind","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lightning"},{"text":", you can specify this at creation:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","text":"Provide a Habitat","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Exercise a Sloth","level":3,"anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity"},{"text":" protocol and implementing the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"]},{"text":"Feed a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food","isActive":true},{"text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"code":"Date","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documen